- **Test-count regression root cause (iter-80 #347)** ŌĆö Investigated 2852 ŌåÆ 2525 passed test "regression." Root cause: **NOT coverlet**. Two test projects (`DINOForge.Tests.CliTools`, `GameLaunch`) had pre-existing CS0234/CS0103 compile errors blocking ~327 test discoveries in normal CI runs. Unrelated to iter-79 closure-gate work. Baseline question "2852 vs 2525" was a red herring.
- **Pattern #333 D1+D2 follow-up audit flagged (#349)** ŌĆö 16 DANGEROUS bare-catch sites converted in iter-79 #333 using comment-only `// safe-swallow: <reason>` approach per governance rule alternatives. Secondary audit #349 needed to verify whether logging injection should be retroactively applied (vs. comment-only compliance).

